  645   /* Function Definitions */
  646   static void b_emlrt_update_log_39(const boolean_T in[2],
  647     emlrtLocationLoggingDataType table[613])
  648   {
  649     boolean_T localMin;
  650     boolean_T localMax;
  651     int32_T i;
  652     localMin = (table[0U].SimMin > 0.0);
  653     localMax = (table[0U].SimMax > 0.0);
  654     for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
  655       /* Simulation Min-Max logging. */
  656       if ((int32_T)in[i] < (int32_T)localMin) {
  657         localMin = in[i];
  658       }
  659   
  660       if ((int32_T)in[i] > (int32_T)localMax) {
  661         localMax = in[i];
  662       }
  663     }
  664   
  665     table[0U].SimMin = localMin;
  666     table[0U].SimMax = localMax;
  667   
  668     /* IsAlwaysInteger logging. */
  669     /* Data type is always integer. */
  670   }
  671   
  672   static void b_emlrt_update_log_40(const emxArray_real_T *in,
  673     emlrtLocationLoggingDataType table[613])
  674   {
  675     real_T localMin;
  676     real_T localMax;
  677     int32_T i;
  678     localMin = table[0U].SimMin;
  679     localMax = table[0U].SimMax;
  680     for (i = 0; i < in->size[0] * in->size[1]; i++) {
  681       /* Simulation Min-Max logging. */
  682       if (in->data[i] < localMin) {
  683         localMin = in->data[i];
  684       }
  685   
  686       if (in->data[i] > localMax) {
  687         localMax = in->data[i];
  688       }
  689     }
  690   
  691     table[0U].SimMin = localMin;
  692     table[0U].SimMax = localMax;
  693   
  694     /* IsAlwaysInteger logging. */
  695     i = 0;
  696     while (table[0U].IsAlwaysInteger && (i < in->size[0] * in->size[1])) {
  697       if (in->data[i] != muDoubleScalarFloor(in->data[i])) {
  698         table[0U].IsAlwaysInteger = false;
  699       }
  700   
  701       i++;
  702     }
  703   }
  704   
  705   static void b_emlrt_update_log_41(const emxArray_real_T *in,
  706     emlrtLocationLoggingDataType table[613])
  707   {
  708     real_T localMin;
  709     real_T localMax;
  710     int32_T i;
  711     localMin = table[0U].SimMin;
  712     localMax = table[0U].SimMax;
  713     for (i = 0; i < in->size[0]; i++) {
  714       /* Simulation Min-Max logging. */
  715       if (in->data[i] < localMin) {
  716         localMin = in->data[i];
  717       }
  718   
  719       if (in->data[i] > localMax) {
  720         localMax = in->data[i];
  721       }
  722     }
  723   
  724     table[0U].SimMin = localMin;
  725     table[0U].SimMax = localMax;
  726   
  727     /* IsAlwaysInteger logging. */
  728     i = 0;
  729     while (table[0U].IsAlwaysInteger && (i < in->size[0])) {
  730       if (in->data[i] != muDoubleScalarFloor(in->data[i])) {
  731         table[0U].IsAlwaysInteger = false;
  732       }
  733   
  734       i++;
  735     }
  736   }

  738   static void emlrt_update_log_39(const boolean_T in[2],
  739     emlrtLocationLoggingDataType table[613], boolean_T out[2])
  740   {
  741     int32_T i62;
  742     for (i62 = 0; i62 < 2; i62++) {
  743       out[i62] = in[i62];
  744     }
  745   
  746     b_emlrt_update_log_39(out, table);
  747   }

  749   static void emlrt_update_log_40(const emlrtStack *sp, const emxArray_real_T *in,
  750     emlrtLocationLoggingDataType table[613], emxArray_real_T *out)
  751   {
  752     int32_T i63;
  753     int32_T loop_ub;
  754     i63 = out->size[0] * out->size[1];
  755     out->size[0] = in->size[0];
  756     out->size[1] = in->size[1];
  757     emxEnsureCapacity(sp, (emxArray__common *)out, i63, (int32_T)sizeof(real_T),
  758                       (emlrtRTEInfo *)NULL);
  759     loop_ub = in->size[0] * in->size[1];
  760     for (i63 = 0; i63 < loop_ub; i63++) {
  761       out->data[i63] = in->data[i63];
  762     }
  763   
  764     b_emlrt_update_log_40(out, table);
  765   }
